---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

// NOTE FOR SAVELLE: This is a plain-language starter policy that reflects the
// site's actual third parties (Google Analytics, Vimeo, Stripe). Have it
// reviewed by counsel and adjust the effective date before relying on it.
const lastUpdated = 'June 9, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Savelle McThias"
  description="How savellem.com collects, uses, and protects your information."
>
  <section class="container-custom py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4 tracking-tight">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-12">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="prose-custom">
        <p>
          This Privacy Policy explains how Savelle McThias (&ldquo;I,&rdquo; &ldquo;me,&rdquo; or
          &ldquo;Savelle LLC&rdquo;) collects, uses, and protects information when you visit
          savellem.com or contact me about design services.
        </p>

        <h2>Information I collect</h2>
        <p><strong>Information you provide.</strong> When you email me, fill out a form, or purchase
          a service, you may share your name, email address, phone number, project details, and—
          for purchases—payment information processed by my payment provider.</p>
        <p><strong>Information collected automatically.</strong> Like most websites, this site uses
          analytics to understand how visitors use it. This may include your approximate location,
          device and browser type, pages viewed, and referring links. This data is aggregated and
          is not used to personally identify you.</p>

        <h2>How I use information</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>To respond to your inquiries and provide design services</li>
          <li>To process payments and deliver purchased deliverables</li>
          <li>To understand and improve how the site performs</li>
          <li>To send information you have requested or that relates to work in progress</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Third-party services</h2>
        <p>This site relies on a few trusted third parties, each governed by its own privacy policy:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — website usage measurement
            (<a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">privacy policy</a>)</li>
          <li><strong>Vimeo</strong> — the embedded portfolio video
            (<a href="https://vimeo.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">privacy policy</a>)</li>
          <li><strong>Stripe</strong> — secure payment processing for purchases
            (<a href="https://stripe.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">privacy policy</a>)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>I do not sell your personal information.</p>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>The site and its analytics and embedded-media providers may use cookies or similar
          technologies. You can control cookies through your browser settings; disabling them may
          affect some features, such as the embedded video.</p>

        <h2>Data retention</h2>
        <p>I keep the information you provide only as long as needed to respond to you, deliver
          services, meet legal and accounting obligations, and resolve disputes.</p>

        <h2>Your choices</h2>
        <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of the personal information you
          have shared with me by emailing the address below. You can also opt out of analytics
          tracking using browser tools or extensions.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about this policy? Email
          <a href="mailto:savellem@gmail.com">savellem@gmail.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
